          <h1>Few words from myself</h1>
          <p>
          Suddenly I realized that I want to travel and write code with other
          people on my road. I am planning a trip in May 2016
          and looking for people who want to meet and pair.
          </p>
          <p>
          Currently the project is under the development.
          <a href="#subscribe" class="page-scroll">Subscribe</a> to be the first one who uses Ruby On Road.
